Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Applies an impulse to the current entity.

Usage
-----

*void* applyImpulse( *entity* **source** , *vector* **point** , *vector* **impulse** )

Parameters
----------

-   [source] -
-   [point] -
-   [impulse] -

Examples
--------

    $my_entity.applyImpulse( $my_entity2, '0 0 90', '0 90 0' );

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.


